Felix the cat disappeared after his crate was damaged on a flight from Abu Dhabi to New York on April 1 . 
  The two-year-old tabby was adopted by Jennifer Stewart and husband Joseph Naaman . 
  The cat escaped from his crate at John F Kennedy International Airport . 
  Couple said the plastic carrier was damaged while being transferred from the plane . 
  Etihad Airways said it is investigating and is working with the couple to find the cat . 
 